TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

The next few problems are exercises in function composition.

Let \[f(x) = 2x+1 \quad\hbox{and}\quad g(x) = x^2-1 \]

$BR

Then 

$BR
A. \((f \circ f) (x) = \) \{ ans_rule(15) \}. $BR
EOT
&ANS( multivar_function_cmp("4*x+3",["x"]));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
B. \((g \circ g) (x) = \) \{ ans_rule(15) \}. $BR
EOT
&ANS( multivar_function_cmp("x^4-2x^2",["x"]));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
C. \((f \circ g) (x) = \) \{ ans_rule(15) \}. $BR
EOT
&ANS( multivar_function_cmp("2x^2-1",["x"]));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
D. \((g \circ f) (x) = \) \{ ans_rule(15) \}.
$BR
EOT
&ANS( multivar_function_cmp("4x^2+4x",["x"]));



